onnect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9592b473ce650c1d82499a5e81154da2e016954","tid":1544912,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"又送錢人洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f440c77648da9f2aa70ff8cc1ecfd2aac6d90dd","tid":1544912,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">YES</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">YES</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">YES</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">YES</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"81eb63d3594993b736f77e6b7065c9d11df849d6","tid":1544912,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"政府打國際輿論戰, 我地唔應戰嗎?"}]}